用盡全身僅有的力氣大聲叫喊「啊啊啊！！啊！噢！噢............噢.................」<br />\n<br />\n        就在7-11收據結束她漫長的據生前，神秘湖泊終於甦醒了，她最後聽到的一句話，就是：「痴撚線，乜撚野貝加爾湖呀屌，呢度叫做箱根呀屌，我係箱根入面嘅一個細細地嘅火山湖黎㗎咋屌，咪撚嘈住我瞓教啦屌，宜家幾點鐘呀屌！叫春就返7-11對住個收銀機叫啦屌！」<br />\n<br />\n        就這樣，可憐的7-11收據只能含冤地於這火山湖體內化成一堆營養，於火山湖體內的古菌孕育出新生命.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">完</div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"我有禮貌啲講句，閣下真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c43b7a9f9849c9a9569522f5f3e9d322db5fc1a","tid":543314,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5f847a76fcd97e823063029ded3749bd92af459","tid":543314,"uid":82688,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"明明作者好忙想個post沉，點解又會推翻上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"射射我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e759a5d54ce7b12ca73dcd4530f31769483ef8","tid":543314,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37810ad2281657e570d367b8ddfa5131da936a77","tid":543314,"uid":105707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"娥姐 同 普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193068d056897d075c746bc8b42dcd48eadbb768","tid":543314,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:22:10.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國+大東亞共榮圈"},{"pid":"61d5a3ed467ccd09bfd56f58397fe25549b0905f","tid":543314,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c7e5703a9e61d3108d882175a13db83a6faf3a29","tid":543314,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a0963951ff1370b848c3d475900378061c904b","tid":543314,"uid":69306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28